title: Molina in lineup for Cardinals in NLDS opener vs. Cubs (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,166 Molina in lineup for Cardinals in NLDS opener vs. Cubs (Yahoo Sports) ST. LOUIS (AP) -- All-Star catcher Yadier Molina is in the lineup batting seventh for the St. Louis Cardinals in the NL Division Series opener against the Chicago Cubs.
